name: Lost Frame
description:
Somewhere in or just out of Transylvania from the window of an old train. January 2008, cold winter, on a Zorki-4. 

Long after I developed photos from this series, I discovered this negative that had been missed, it was a missing piece of my voice in the way I shot those years that I can't replicate any more. So I'll start with it here, this is my "alpha" drop, in a series of a few first tries before I get the hang of this.
